    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_527863">If anyone is into Blue Mountain yet, spend some time in the Ak'Ab Abyss. (Quest: Enemy of my Enemy 3/5) The drop rate inside the cave is insane. There are pods you can two shot that often drop runes or gear, and the enemies they spawn are weak and often drop loot themselves. And the pods respawn. <br />
<br />
Didn't see any blue quality loot after the hour I spent in there, but man I got a ton of mats and a lot of runes I desparately need to make stuff. I think I walked out of there with at least 12 tank runes, enough that I'm contemplating building a tanking set. I also picked up about 8 Gadget patterns. QL 5 as far as the eye can see.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
