    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_527939">I do way less than that per hit, but many of my blood abilities crit and pen for about 500. And I can drop those things really fast. TBH the damage over time on Blood abilities, even with the passives to boost the damage, seem to be pale in comparison to the DD it's capable of. I gave up Left Hand of Darkness which is a 90 damage dot every second for 3 seconds, because I can crank out 2x to 3x that amount of damage with one successful crit or pen on a DD ability.<br />
<br />
