<br />
This buddy key is good to allow one of your friends to join you for 24 hours in The Secret World. Once you have sent your buddy key out, your friend will receive an email with a key attached. All they have to do is follow the instructions in the email and they'll be ready to fight with you against the encroaching darkness!<br />
<br />
You'll have to act fast since this offer is only valid until Sunday the 15th of July! If you have pre-ordered, but have not yet received your game key, you will not have a buddy invite available. However, as soon as you upgrade your account with a game key, you will receive a buddy invite to share with a friend. Your friend's 24 hours does not start until they first log into the client.<br />
