    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_533296">The Secret World is going to a Guild Wars style payment model in where you pay for the game and no longer have to pay for a monthly fee.  Those who want to pay a monthly fee or those with a lifetime subscription get these bonuses:<br />
<br />
 Unique Membership-only item which increases experience gain for defeating monster by 100% for 1 hour each day<br />
$10 worth of Bonus Points (given out every month)*<br />
Membership Item-of-the-month gift (given out every month)<br />
10% discount to everything in the Item Store<br />
 * Bonus points are valid for 6 months and can be used towards any product in the Item Store of The Secret World<br />
 ** Discounts to the Item Store do not stack with other offers<br />
<br />
<br />
Also, they've started a new ARG which begins <a href="http://situationroom.thesecretworld.com/" target="_blank">here</a>.</div>
